[BEGIN]
module TopModule (
    input logic clk,
    input logic reset,
    output logic [4:0] q
);

    always_ff @(posedge clk) begin
        if (reset) begin
            q <= 5'b00001;
        end else begin
            q[4:1] <= q[3:0];
            q[0] <= q[4] ^ q[2];
        end
    end

endmodule
